This paper focuses on improving the performance of a computational package for persistent homology, which is a method for analyzing topological features of data. This topic is closely related to computer science sub-categories such as data structures (cs.DS), computational geometry (cs.CG), numerical analysis (cs.NA), scientific computing (cs.SC), and systems and control (cs.SY).
